sources.description:
No One Can Survive His Flames | Fireball | Full Action Movie - Ava Williams, a skilled fire inspector following in her fatherâ€™s footsteps, has faced every blaze imaginable, until a mysterious fire tears through the local jail. Tasked with leading the investigation, she encounters cocky Federal Investigator Lee Cooper and soon learns that the fire is just the beginning. Tyler Draven, a dangerous celebrity and experimental sports drug addict, has narrowly survived the inferno and is now on a vengeful rampage, setting deadly fires and hurling fireballs across the city. Racing against time, Ava and Cooper must put aside their differences, unravel the clues, and confront a man willing to destroy everything in his path. To stop him before he reaches a nuclear power plant, they will have to fight fire with fire.

2009.  Stars: Ian Somerhalder, Lexa Doig, Aleks Paunovic
